**Minimal (Specialist)**:
```yaml
skills:
  - name: code-review-patterns
    path: task/code-review-patterns
    required: true
    description: Code review best practices

skills_loading: progressive
max_skills_loaded: 1
```

**Moderate (Hybrid)**:
